We're looking forward to attending the London to Brighton EV Rally this Saturday. We'll be on Madeira Drive in Brighton showcasing the all-new MAXUS eDeliver 7 and MIFA 9.

The rally and it's partners play a massive role in demystifying electric vehicles, with experts on-hand to answer questions, showcase the latest in EV technology, charging solutions and more, it's a great event to attend, with lots of custom builds and latest models from a variety of manufacturers.

